Description: A unique ID for the sampling event, preferably as "<cruiseID>#<event number>". For example: 64PE438#21.
The date when the sampling event took place in the format "DD/MM/YYYY". For example: 12/01/1994.
Latitude of the dredge when the dredge touched bottom.
Longitude of the dredge when the dredge touched bottom.
Latitude of the dredge when the dredge was heaved from the bottom.
Longitude of the dredge when the dredge was heaved from the bottom.
Closest approximation possible of the latitude of the midpoint of the dredge track.
Closest approximation possible of the longitude of the midpoint of the dredge track.
Track length as measured by the odometer.
Generic name of the station where the sample is taken.
Time when the dredge touched bottom.
Time when the dredge was heaved from the bottom.
Water depth at the start (??) of the dredge track.
Length of cable veered from ship to the dredge.
Qualitative description of the quality of the dredge.
